This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it focuses on vision-based object detection in traffic scenes. The use of deep networks also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of self-driving vehicle systems and advance driver assistance systems (ADAS) suggests that it could also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the mention of efficiency and resource constraints suggests that it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
